arts.ttl: PLAYER RATINGS: How did Carlisle United fare at Harrogate?
arts.sum: RATINGS: How did we score the players in Carlisle United's miserable 1-0 defeat at Harrogate Town?

arts.ttl: Latest on injury that ruled striker Dennis out of Carlisle United defeat
arts.sum: Striker Matt Dennis is likely to have a scan on his hamstring after missing Carlisle United's 1-0 defeat to Harrogate Town.

arts.ttl: Ellis Taylor scores stoppage-time winner for Harrogate to beat ailing Carlisle
arts.sum: The Cumbrians are now six points adrift of safety at the foot of the League Two table – albeit with a game in hand.

arts.ttl: Carlisle United suffer injury-time defeat at Harrogate
arts.sum: REPORT: Carlisle United's survival hopes suffered a severe blow as bogey side Harrogate struck in the 94th minute to win 1-0.

arts.ttl: Former Carlisle United defender makes National League move
arts.sum: Former Carlisle United defender Josh Emmanuel has made a move to the National League.

Harrogate's 0-0 draw with Port Vale on Tuesday night was their second game without defeat, and they have now just lost once in their last three games. Carlisle's 1-1 draw with Walsall on Tuesday nigh...

arts.ttl: Hughes sheds more light on coach's departure at Carlisle United
arts.sum: Mark Hughes has explained that the latest coaching change at Carlisle United was made with the “dynamic” of the group in mind.

arts.ttl: Carlisle United confirm timing of season ticket decision
arts.sum: Carlisle United say they will not make a decision on season ticket prices and plans until they know what division they will be in next term.

arts.ttl: In pictures: Carlisle United fans at the Walsall game!
arts.sum: GALLERY: Check out Richard Parkes' brilliant fan photos as 6,378 watched Carlisle United's 1-1 draw with leaders Walsall at Brunton Park.

arts.ttl: Hughes on Carlisle United's bid to break Harrogate jinx
arts.sum: Mark Hughes says records are there to be broken as Carlisle United bid to break their Harrogate Town duck this weekend.
